      <h2 xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> <span class="mw-headline" id="Box_office_performance">Box office performance</span></h2>
      <h2 xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> <span class="mw-headline" id="Academy_Awards">Academy Awards</span></h2>
      <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Paymer was nominated for an <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academy_Award_for_Best_Supporting_Actor" title="Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor">Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor</a> for his performance. He lost to <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gene_Hackman" title="Gene Hackman">Gene Hackman</a> for <i><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unforgiven" title="Unforgiven">Unforgiven</a></i>.</p>
